<%= partial "template_top" %>

<main class="wrapper">

  <div class="row column">
    <div class="callout secondary mb-sm">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Saepe aperiam, et sit, suscipit, porro quibusdam enim doloremque voluptatibus cum dolores qui incidunt obcaecati voluptate velit, corrupti vero dolorem ea quos.</p>
